data.description: Englewood Charmer. This cottage style home has hardwood floors, a wood fireplace and new Laminate Vinyl Plank in the Kitchen and bath. Lots of trees in this neighborhood. Super deep yard with lots of native plants and room for a large garden.  It has access alley access to the back yard making it easy for gardening.  Workshop and laundry are in the garage. This home is a must see.
